casebody.data:
Tonya RATHELL, fka Tonya Chakkour, petitioner,
v.
Ahmed CHAKKOUR. No. 12-10108. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until October 28, 2013, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule *37838(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
